{"tid":989381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(慎入)誤信偏方！花露水洗目睭　婦角膜爛膿穿孔摘眼球","createTime":"2019-01-20T21:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T06:42:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"eadef33863dba644991b5b16022117655c50101a","tid":989381,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T21:12:06.000Z","msg":"江西南昌一名6旬婦人左眼不太舒服，竟聽信村民偏方，用青菜汁拌鹽、還用花露水洗眼睛，結果眼睛越洗越痛，受不了了才就醫，但角膜已潰爛流膿，甚至穿孔，醫師迫不得已摘除她的左眼球。<br />\n中國媒體報導，婦人十多天前覺得左眼不太舒服，頻流眼淚、眼睛發紅，當地村民介紹她用青菜汁拌鹽、花露水洗眼睛消解發炎，為了不上醫院省錢，婦人真的照辦，洗著洗著眼睛卻越洗越痛。<br />\n負責診治的醫師表示，當婦人就醫時，角膜已經非常薄了，而且還潰爛流膿，隔天角膜穿孔，只好摘除眼球。如果當時立刻看醫生，只要一、兩瓶藥水就能控制。婦人的家屬也念她「有錢買不到眼睛」，為了省錢，現在後悔也來不及了。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190121/640_7c97205d15761e7a125b6a2985696414.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190121%2F640_7c97205d15761e7a125b6a2985696414.jpg&h=19251d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190121/640_184094bc13f8522a99090d86a96f578d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190121%2F640_184094bc13f8522a99090d86a96f578d.jpg&h=bfd91b47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190121/1504264/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190121%2F1504264%2F&d=LmeMrEZh8tz9lmG61MNcsv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=047ae8c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190121%2F1504264%2F&h=9ad48d28\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190121/1504264/</a>"},{"pid":"8c71baaefa155c01b66de0f0bfb3ff0e46417e62","tid":989381,"uid":147245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T21:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha